vietnam 's armi order to grow more food vietnam ha order it armi to grow more food to eas shortag and meet econom recoveri goal set for 1990. the armi newspap quan doi nhan dan , monitor here , said soldier must work harder to care for rice , veget and other crop endang by the present unusu hot weather . the paper said the 1.6-mln strong regular armi contribut less than one pct to the nation 's 18.2 mln tonn food output . north vietnam ha set a 1990 food target of 23 to 24 mln tonn .